就要理解是什么带来改变然后去做

64
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:31,380
Spread the word.
传播理念

65
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:35,120
Spread the word about the research.
传播研究的理念

66
00:04:35,590 --> 00:04:40,710
Even if the research doesn't always communicate good news,
即使研究并非总是传达好消息

67
00:04:40,710 --> 00:04:42,840
it's about communicating what works,
它传达的是行之有效的方法

68
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:45,570
what is real, as opposed to our dreams ,
可为的方式而不是空洞的梦想

69
00:04:45,570 --> 00:04:49,220
our desires, our hopes, our wishes--
渴望 希望 愿望

70
00:04:49,220 --> 00:04:50,780
that's not enough.
那远远不够

71
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:55,810
Good will, idealism, good intentions are not enough.
好的意愿 理想主义 好的意图是不够的

72
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:58,850
