我喜欢这个说法

84
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:37,970
Democratizing excellence--
将杰出大众化

85
00:05:38,250 --> 00:05:43,560
studying the best and applying it to the rest of us.
研究最好的再应用在其他人身上

86
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:49,200
