我们有了这样一个伟大的计划

87
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:52,060
grand idea by Maslow to create a Manhattan-type Project.
有了Maslow创造类似曼哈顿计划的伟大想法

88
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:55,860
But what if I'm not interested in going into one of these projects?
