Someone smiles-- makes you smile.
别人笑会引起你发笑

132
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:27,700
You smile-- you make someone smile.
你发笑会引起别人发笑

133
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,500
And so on and so on.
以此类推

134
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:34,130
You know, even some goes pass you on the street and you don't smile
即使路人与你擦身而过时 你没笑

135
00:08:34,810 --> 00:08:36,160
ostensibly you don't smile--
表面上你没有笑

136
