145
00:09:03,310 --> 00:09:07,130
Within 20 degrees of separation from you
只需要20度的分隔

146
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:09,660
initial smile to the three people,
从你用笑容感染三个人开始

147
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,200
the entire world will be smiling.
全世界就会笑起来

148
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:20,660
Exponential nature of social networks.
社会网络的指数本质

149
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:24,230
The same with making other people feel good--
让别人感觉良好也有感染力

150
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:25,760
complimenting people.
恭维别人

151
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,940
If you make three people--
如果你能让三个人

152
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:31,480
or even better, four people a day feel good and they make--
甚至四个人度过美妙的一天

153
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:34,630
