This is something I've working on for many years
这是我多年努力的目标

384
00:22:35,150 --> 00:22:36,460
and this will be it.
这将会是

385
00:22:36,460 --> 00:22:38,190
This will be a dream come true."
将是梦想成真"

386
00:22:38,570 --> 00:22:41,530
And-- "How happy are you going to stay for?"
"你会快乐多久?"

387
