And then he went to those who didn't get tenure and asked them,
然后他去找没得到终身职位的并问

416
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:04,410
"How are you feeling?"
"你们感觉如何?"

417
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:06,600
They were devastated.
他们很难过

418
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:07,880
And they were sure that
而且确信

419
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:11,500
