会难过好久

420
00:24:13,020 --> 00:24:18,180
And he went back to see them three months later,
三个月后 他再去访问他们

421
00:24:18,330 --> 00:24:19,980
six months later.
六个月后再去

422
00:24:21,590 --> 00:24:25,500
And what Gilbert and his colleagues found
Gilbert和他的同事发现

